    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Up for sale is a well-maintained vehicle in good overall condition, perfect for someone looking for a reliable and attractive daily driver. Mechanically, the car is solid with a consistent service history, though the interior shows light wear on the driver's seat and the exterior has a few minor stone chips on the front bumper. All major systems, including the air conditioning and electronics, are fully functional. This is a great opportunity to own a dependable vehicle that has been cared for properly without the 'mint' price tag.",
