    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and has served as a reliable daily driver. The exterior shows noticeable signs of age, including several scratches, some fading in the clear coat, and a few minor dings. Inside, the upholstery shows significant wear and some staining, though all essential controls remain functional. While it runs and drives, a potential buyer should expect to address some upcoming maintenance items and cosmetic touch-ups to bring it back to its best.",
